name: sling_bikini_top
description:
I really like this style of bikini and I couldn't find it on Civitai, so here you go!

Limited testing showed that 0.6-0.8 works well, use "sling_bikini_top" as a trigger word and optionally add "bikini".

This is my first upload, so any kind of feedback is welcome!
